race.description: Sportsbet Supporters Of Having A Crack
race.comment: TENNESSEE KADE (7) lines up chasing another win after sizzling around Ballarat over 450m in 25.07 on October 30. Rates a top chance again if runs up to latest. LIKE A ROCK (5) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his enormous 29.43 win at Sandown over 515m. Expecting another bold showing. LANDED (3) is one of the chances after a minor prize from this draw last time.
